sql:
SELECT page_name 
FROM pages 
WHERE page_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
- "Captains of the administrative ship" metaphorically refers to users with the 'admin' role; 
- "Voyages" metaphorically refers to different event types; 
- "Steered their voyages most successfully" refers to the success rate of each event type; 
- "How smoothly did each journey go" refers to the success rate of each event type, calculated as the percentage of successful events out of total events.
